**** reloading powernow-k8 driver, to check if cpufreq-info gets back working
# rmmod powernow-k8
# modprobe powernow-k8
FATAL: Error inserting powernow_k8 
(/lib/modules/2.6.20-ARCH/kernel/arch/i386/kernel/cpu/cpufreq/powernow-k8.ko): 
No such device
